ty":"sha512-yodFGwcyt59XRh7w5W3jPcIQb3Bwi21suEfT7MAWnBX3iCdklJpgDgvGT9o04UonglZN5SNMfJFkHIR/jO8GHw==","signatures":[{"keyid":"SHA256:jl3bwswu80PjjokCgh0o2w5c2U4LhQAE57gj9cz1kzA","sig":"MEYCIQDaoPJYVS8c1WNkdsuoyiMFq4CdLPiXBmV89WA4FSZsyQIhAN+gu7MT4gv3dtwVzKINOSkonC32bYLQ1N2jxPsUsYmz"}]},"_from":".","_npmVersion":"1.4.3","_npmUser":{"name":"mikolalysenko","email":"mikolalysenko@gmail.com"},"maintainers":[{"name":"mikolalysenko","email":"mikolalysenko@gmail.com"}]}},"readme":"signum\n======\nReturns the sign of a floating point number\n\n# Example\n\n```javascript\nvar sgn = require(\"signum\")\n\nconsole.log(sgn(-0.00001))\nconsole.log(sng(0))\nconsole.log(sng(Infinity))\n```\n\nOutput:\n\n```javascript\n-1\n0\n1\n```\n\n# Install\n\n```\nnpm install signum\n```\n\n# API\n\n### `require(\"signum\")(x)`\nReturns the sign of `x`\n\n* `x` is a number\n\n**Returns** One of the following values\n\n* `-1` if `x<0`\n* `1` if `x>0`\n* `0` otherwise\n\n# Credits\n(c) 2014 Mikola Lysenko. MIT License\n","maintainers":[{"name":"mikolalysenko","email":"mikolalysenko@gmail.com"}],"time":{"modified":"2022-06-26T19:22:44.327Z","created":"2014-03-30T17:10:42.321Z","0.0.0":"2014-03-30T17:10:42.321Z","1.0.0":"2014-04-30T01:37:44.383Z"},"homepage":"https://github.com/mikolalysenko/signum","keywords":["sign","number","signum","plus","minus","zero"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git://github.com/mikolalysenko/signum.git"},"author":{"name":"Mikola Lysenko"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/mikolalysenko/signum/issues"},"license":"MIT","readmeFilename":"README.md"}